import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { UserService } from '../../services/user.service'; import { User } from 'src/app/models/user'; import { Observable } from 'rxjs'; @Component({ selector: 'app-user', templateUrl: './user.component.html', styleUrls: ['./user.component.scss'] }) export class UserComponent { user: User = { name: '', surname: '', birthDate: '', email: '', phoneNumber: '' }; constructor(private userService: UserService) {} saveUser(): void { const data = { name: this.user.name, surname: this.user.surname, birthDate: this.user.birthDate, email: this.user.email, phoneNumber: this.user.phoneNumber }; this.userService.create(data).subscribe({ next: (res) => { console.log(res); }, error: (e) => console.error(e) }); } }
